Issues.Body:
As per documentation (https://tailwindcss.com/docs/flex), I tried to extend the flex utilities, like:

```js
module.exports = {
  theme: {
    extend: {
      flex: {
        '2': '2 2 0%'
      }
    }
  }
}
```

However, I always received the message, the class cannot be found when I tried to use it with @apply like

```sass
@apply tw-flex-2 
```

